reviewText: Platinum Comedy Series are timeless and amazing on live Comedy Stand-Up. Both Adele Givens & D.L. Hughley deliver amazing non-stop eye-tearing laughing DVD with high quality with no issues just straight healing your painful days with deep soul hard laughing that you almost unable to breathe that's what exactly I was looking for and virally worth the money to buy it.

I get D L and Adele in a package? WOW! Who do I like best? Hard to say. D L is alright. I think he is one of the best out there today. I even think he'd be just as humorous without the profanity. But, that's me. Adele on the other hand is hilarious and thought provoking. And, her poems really touch the heart.
